This marks the initial alpha 1 release of RubyGems.

For user documentation (and installation instructions) see:

./doc/UserDoc.html

For developer docs see:

./doc/DevDoc.html
./doc/GemSpecification.html

All of these documents (in there latest versions) are available on 
the RubyGems wiki at:

http://rubygems.rubyforge.org

Additional directories:

./bin/...      binary commands (gem, gem_server, etc)
./lib/...      the RubyGems library
./packages/... default RubyGems packages (currently only 'sources')
./test/...     unit tests
./example/...  example library w/gemspec for generating and installing gems
./gemspecs/... example gemspecs

